Pseudocode structure of database 

Note that we can use the SQL type TEXT for the blog text. 

I think we should split this up into threes and each do a section. We should be able to do this today.

Post
	Post ID (primary key)
	Title
	Subtitle
	Short title
	Summary
	Text

Blog
	Title (primary key)
	Slogan
	Owner (a user)

User
	Username (primary key)
	Location
	Name
	Email address

Subscription
	User
	Blog

Authorship
	Post
	User

Readership
	Post
	User

Posting
	Post
	Blog

Comment
	User
	Post
	Date
